function Menu({ logoSrc }) {
    return ( <
        header >
        <
        nav className = "navbar navbar-expand-lg" >
        <
        a href = "#"
        class = "navbar-brand" >
        <
        img src = { logoSrc }
        alt = "Playcell"
        id = "brand-logo" / >
        <
        /a> <
        /nav> <
        /header>
    );
}
export default Menu
